# Frontend

- Routes: `frontend/src/routes/` — `_public/` guest, `_authenticated/` auth later
- Hooks: `frontend/src/hooks/` — all API via TanStack Query (`useCart`, `useWishlist`, …)
- No fetch/axios in components
- Zustand: cart drawer UI + wishlist badge count; server data in Query
- shadcn + Tailwind; Amazon tokens in `index.css` / `tailwind.config.ts`
- Search typeahead: `useSearchSuggestions` (debounced, not Query)
- Responsive: mobile-first breakpoints; `MobileMenu` for nav on `<md`; stack layouts until `lg:`
- Wishlist: `WishlistButton`, `WishlistItem`, page at `_authenticated/wishlist.tsx`

New feature: types → hook → component → route
